oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Michael (Bo) Milsaps interview
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Milsaps, Michael; Caudill, Ed
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Milsaps, Michael; Vietnam War, 1961-1975
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Michael Millsaps served as a Corporal in the U.S. Marine Corps during the Vietnam War from February 1969 to August 1970. The interview was conducted by Ed Caudill on May 21, 2019 at the Blount County Public Library.
